    "question_id" : 288861,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>In Eclipse 4.9, you can static import existing invocations using a quick fix.</p>\n\n<blockquote>\n  <p>A new quick fix has been implemented that allows the user to convert static field accesses and static methods to use a static import. It's also possible to replace all occurrences at the same time.</p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.eclipse.org/eclipse/news/4.9/jdt.php#convert-to-static-import\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">More details here</a></p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 465839,
      "reputation" : 6815,
      "user_id" : 870207,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "accept_rate" : 0,
