    "score" : 2,
    "last_activity_date" : 1539358124,
    "creation_date" : 1539358124,
    "answer_id" : 52782688,
    "question_id" : 288861,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Select the constant, type</p>\n\n<pre><code>Ctrl + 1  (quick fix)\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Select \"Convert to static import.\" from the drop down.</p>\n\n<p>\"Quick fix\" has options even though it is not an error.</p>\n"
